      "text": "Smart Learning for All"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 7440.0,
      "end_time": 9360.0,
      "text": "Why is the ocean blue?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 9740.0,
      "end_time": 12840.0,
      "text": "Because ocean water reflects blue color of the sky."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 13900.0,
      "end_time": 16600.0,
      "text": "You are right, but not completely."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 17240.0,
      "end_time": 23520.0,
      "text": "The main reason for oceans to be blue is the way water molecules absorb and scatter the colors of sunlight."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23920.0,
      "end_time": 25920.0,
      "text": "Sunlight has seven visible colors."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26340.0,
      "end_time": 31160.0,
      "text": "They are red, orange, yellow, green, blue, indigo and violet."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31640.0,
      "end_time": 32640.0,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32640.0,
      "end_time": 34350.0,
      "text": "I saw them in a rainbow."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34350.0,
      "end_time": 39089.0,
      "text": "Now, when sunlight falls on the ocean, it passes deep into the water."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39089.0,
      "end_time": 43280.0,
      "text": "Here, red, orange, yellow and green colors of sunlight."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43280.0,
      "end_time": 46100.0,
      "text": "Are absorbed more strongly by water molecules."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46170.0,
      "end_time": 50820.0,
      "text": "While, blue, indigo and violet colors are not absorbed much."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50820.0,
      "end_time": 55450.0,
      "text": "Instead, they are scattered, making the ocean appear blue to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55450.0,
      "end_time": 62120.0,
      "text": "However, as the blue shades penetrate deeper into the ocean, eventually they also get absorbed."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62120.0,
      "end_time": 66560.0,
      "text": "Hence, at greater depths the ocean is completely dark."
    },
    {
